re performant for large datasets?','[\"cursor-based pagination\", \"offset-based pagination\", \"full-scan pagination\", \"page-number only pagination\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ee3627-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Name one drawback of offset-based pagination.','[\"Offset pagination can be slow for large offsets and may return inconsistent results if the underlying dataset changes between requests.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ef5d76-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which token type is commonly stored in localStorage for SPA auth (though with security caveats)?','[\"JWT\", \"Session ID cookie\", \"Opaque database key\", \"CSRF token\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73efb3d2-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Give one security risk of storing JWT in localStorage.','[\"LocalStorage is vulnerable to XSS; malicious scripts can read tokens and exfiltrate them.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f06ca1-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which library is commonly used in Node to sign and verify JWTs?','[\"jsonwebtoken\", \"jwt-node\", \"express-jwt\", \"body-jwt\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f0b460-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','A JWT must be encrypted to be secure.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',1,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f14d7f-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which package helps set secure HTTP headers in Express?','[\"helmet\", \"cors\", \"morgan\", \"express-rate-limit\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f19790-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','CORS configuration is only needed for browsers and not for server-to-server requests.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f2993c-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which tool is commonly used for end-to-end HTTP testing of Express apps?','[\"supertest\", \"mocha-http\", \"http-tester\", \"express-test\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f2deee-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Why are integration tests with a running server useful for APIs?','[\"They test the actual HTTP layer, middleware integration, routing and serialization, catching issues that unit tests of handlers may miss.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f36858-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which package is commonly used for request logging in Express?','[\"morgan\", \"winston-express\", \"log4js-express\", \"express-logger\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f3af27-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','Rate limiting should be applied globally and sometimes per-route for sensitive endpoints.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f48e96-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','What is the 12-factor recommendation for storing config?','[\"In environment variables\", \"In source code\", \"In a local JSON file tracked in git\", \"In user input at runtime\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f4d791-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','How should secrets be provided to a containerized app in production?','[\"Use orchestration secrets (Kubernetes Secrets), environment variables injected by CI/CD, or secret managers (AWS Secrets Manager, HashiCorp Vault), not checked-in files.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f57455-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which logger is known for being very fast and JSON-friendly?','[\"pino\", \"console.log\", \"morgan\", \"winston (legacy)\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f5bcde-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','Structured logs (JSON) are easier to query and parse in log aggregators than plain text logs.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f67478-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which of the following is NOT typically part of an API production checklist?','[\"Unrestricted debug logs enabled\", \"Health checks configured\", \"Proper error reporting\", \"Rate limiting for public endpoints\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f6cede-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Name two items you should test before deploying an API.','[\"Examples: behavior under load (performance), authentication flows, critical route responses, error handling, and security checks such as CORS and input validation.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f786e8-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which status code is appropriate for validation errors?','[\"400\", \"200\", \"500\", \"401\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f7d567-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Why centralize error handling in an Express app?','[\"Centralization ensures consistent responses, easier logging and reporting, and avoids duplicated error-to-response mapping across many routes.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f85c20-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which is a good cache location for API responses that don\'t contain private data?','[\"CDN edge cache\", \"Local app memory only\", \"Client localStorage only\", \"Never cache\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f89696-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','Horizontal scaling often requires stateless application design or externalizing session storage.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('742a4776-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','What does the Python statement print(\"Hello, World!\") do when executed?','[\"Outputs the text Hello, World! to the console\", \"Declares a function named Hello, World!\", \"Creates a variable with the value Hello, World!\", \"Starts the Python interpreter\"]',0,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('742ede82-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which of the following is an example of a float data type in Python?','[\"\\\"Hello\\\"\", \"10\", \"3.14\", \"True\"]',2,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('74319edb-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','During Python installation, the course recommends ensuring which option is checked?','[\"Install sample projects\", \"Add Python to PATH\", \"Enable automatic updates\", \"Install only for administrator\"]',1,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('7433e6d5-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which command, shown in the course material, verifies that Python is installed and displays the version?','[\"python --version\", \"check-python\", \"python install --check\", \"show version python\"]',0,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('74366ec1-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which of the following is a valid Python variable name based on typical naming rules and examples in the course?','[\"1age\", \"favorite-color\", \"age_1\", \"my name\"]',2,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('743905d5-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which group of IDEs is mentioned in the course as common tools for writing Python code?','[\"Notepad, Sublime Text, Emacs\", \"VS Code, PyCharm, Jupyter\", \"Eclipse, NetBeans, IntelliJ\", \"Xcode, Android Studio, Visual Studio\"]',1,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('743bc61d-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','Python is described in the course as an interpreted programming language.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('743e0b1b-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','The course advises that checking \"Add Python to PATH\" during installation is unnecessary.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',1,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('7440f9be-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Write the Python statement that prints: Welcome to the Python course!','[\"print(\\\"Welcome to the Python course!\\\")\"]',0,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('74431f67-51db-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','4f0dd6ed-2076-11f1-97b2-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'fb9e6f39-4f78-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Create variables for name = Mika, age = 27, and favorite_color = gray, then write a print statement that outputs: My name is Mika, I am 27 years old, and my favorite color is gray.','[\"name = \\\"Mika\\\"\\nage = 27\\nfavorite_color = \\\"gray\\\"\\nprint(f\\\"My name is {name}, I am {age} years old, and my favorite color is {favorite_color}.\\\")\"]',0,'2026-05-17 13:30:41','2026-05-17 13:30:41'),('7bb5c638-4fcf-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','List three tools or technologies used in this course and why they are useful.','[\"node.js for runtime/npm for packages/git for version control/postman for testing apis\"]',0,'2026-05-14 22:59:57','2026-05-14 22:59:57'),('7bb76937-4fcf-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which command initializes a new npm project interactively?','[\"npm create\", \"npm init\", \"npm start\", \"node init\"]',1,'2026-05-14 22:59:57','2026-05-14 22:59:57'),('7bb824d2-4fcf-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5c