rse describe Python?','[\"Low-level and compiled\", \"High-level and interpreted\", \"High-level and a markup language\", \"Compiled only\"]',1,NULL,1,1,'2026-05-23 20:21:09'),('69cae1cc-ef90-441a-b739-704ab538ce3f','ed45211e-c166-45e7-8f96-ecc7c38b3fba','36d348f5-56cd-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which of the following is the correct way to print the text Hello, World! in Python 3?','[\"print(\\\"Hello, World!\\\")\", \"echo \\\"Hello, World!\\\"\", \"System.out.println(\\\"Hello, World!\\\")\", \"printf(\\\"Hello, World!\\\")\"]',0,NULL,0,1,'2026-05-23 20:33:57'),('6a90646e-ca2a-449f-81a4-fc62f269720d','5c63acbb-2be9-4af0-bc1b-6073963f9163','6a03e6be-56ca-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which of the following is a common field where Python is widely used (as stated in the course)?','[\"Web development\", \"Concrete mixing\", \"Hairdressing\", \"Automobile assembly line work\"]',0,NULL,0,1,'2026-06-01 22:46:23'),('8d46831b-44db-4e4e-b9ab-53a79962aabf','ed45211e-c166-45e7-8f96-ecc7c38b3fba','36e3cab0-56cd-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','In Python, indentation is used to define blocks of code (for example, the body of a function or a loop).','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,NULL,0,1,'2026-05-23 20:33:57'),('977fe025-273f-44e5-8b93-6b2c8ceeb05f','5c63acbb-2be9-4af0-bc1b-6073963f9163','f2ebc085-56c9-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Write the exact output produced by this Python statement: print(\"Welcome to the Python course!\")','[\"Welcome to the Python course!\"]',NULL,'ui',0,0,'2026-06-01 22:46:23'),('b00e6e5c-db29-4472-89f3-cf22a2113e16','ed45211e-c166-45e7-8f96-ecc7c38b3fba','36e84b57-56cd-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','What is the exact output produced by this Python statement? print(\"Welcome to the Python course!\")','[\"Welcome to the Python course!\"]',NULL,'لل',0,0,'2026-05-23 20:33:57'),('b8338d3e-49ca-40a6-8d65-ba135575aaee','5c63acbb-2be9-4af0-bc1b-6073963f9163','f4603412-56c9-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','True or Fa